title: Blinken says Russia's 'playbook' for an invasion of Ukraine is moving forward but war can still be averted - CNN
content:
1. Blinken says Russia's 'playbook' for an invasion of Ukraine is moving forward but war can still be averted  CNN
  2. Blinken: US national security council to meet as Russia Ukraine invasion looms  The Guardian
  3. Sunday shows preview: Russia-Ukraine crisis dominates as White House is 'convinced' of an invasion | TheHill  The Hill
  4. View Full Coverage on Google News
description: Secretary of State Antony Blinken said Sunday that Russia's "playbook" for an invasion of Ukraine is moving forward, though he said there still is a chance for diplomacy to avert a war.
